XX15 N004 Vdd S4 Vee invx1
XX16 P_4 Co_3 Vdd Vee N004 xnor2x1
XX17 N017 Vdd N018 Vee invx1
XX18 P_4 G_3 Vdd N017 Vee nand2x1
XX25 P_1 P_2 Co_0 Vdd Vee N015 3-nand
XX26 P_2 P_3 G_1 Vdd Vee N010 3-nand
XX27 P_3 P_4 G_2 Vdd Vee N019 3-nand
XX29 P_1 P_2 P_3 Co_0 Vdd Vee N012 4-nand
XX30 P_2 P_3 P_4 G_1 Vdd Vee N020 4-nand
XX50 P_1 P_2 P_3 P_4 Co_0 Vdd Vee N022 5-nand
XX5 N006 G_1 Vdd Vee N009 pseudonor-2
XX7 N008 N010 N012 G_3 Vdd Vee N011 pseudonor-4
XX8 N018 N019 N020 N022 G_4 Vdd Vee N021 pseudonor-5
XX10 N009 Vdd Co_1 Vee invx1
XX11 N011 Vdd Co_3 Vee invx1
XX12 N021 Vdd Co_4 Vee invx1
XX13 N016 Vdd Co_2 Vee invx1
XX6 N014 N015 G_2 Vdd Vee N016 pseudonor-3
V1 S0 P_0 0
.param a=0.7
.ends pseudo-cla-5bit-nocin

.subckt pseudo-cla-4bit-nocin A_0 A_1 A_2 A_3 B_0 B_1 B_2 B_3 Vdd Vee Co_3 S0 S1 S2 S3
XX47 P_1 Co_0 Vdd Vee N013 xnor2x1
XX48 P_2 Co_1 Vdd Vee N007 xnor2x1
XX49 P_3 Co_2 Vdd Vee N001 xnor2x1
XX1 A_0 B_0 Vdd Vee G_0 P_0 pg
XX2 A_1 B_1 Vdd Vee G_1 P_1 pg
XX3 A_2 B_2 Vdd Vee G_2 P_2 pg
XX4 A_3 B_3 Vdd Vee G_3 P_3 pg
V1 Co_0 G_0 0
