XX19 N009 Vdd Co_3 Vee invx1
XX20 N001 Vdd S3 Vee invx1
XX21 N007 Vdd S2 Vee invx1
XX22 N013 Vdd S1 Vee invx1
XX6 N003 G_1 Vdd Vee N006 pseudonor-2
XX7 N012 N014 G_2 Vdd Vee N015 pseudonor-3
